#: inc/settings-display.php:76
msgid ""
"How to use the plugin: 1. <a href=https://www.finteza.com/en/register data-"
"target=registration target=_blank>Register</a> an account in Finteza; 2. "
"Save the generated website ID in the settings; 3. Configure tracking of link "
"click events; 4. View your website visit statistics in the <a href=https://"
"panel.finteza.com target=_blank>Finteza dashboard</a>"
msgstr ""
"How to use the plugin:\n"
"\n"
"1. <a href=https://www.finteza.com/en/register?utm_source=wordpress."
"admin&utm_medium=link&utm_term=finteza.register&utm_content=finteza.plugin."
"wordpress&utm_campaign=finteza.wordpress data-target=registration "
"target=_blank>Register</a> an account in Finteza\n"
"2. Save the generated website ID in the settings\n"
"3. Configure tracking of link click events\n"
"4. View your website visit statistics in the <a href=https://panel.finteza."
"com?utm_source=wordpress.admin&utm_medium=link&utm_content=finteza.plugin."
"wordpress&utm_term=finteza.panel&utm_campaign=finteza.wordpress "
"target=_blank>Finteza dashboard</a>"

#: inc/settings-display.php:83
msgid "How to track clicks"
msgstr "How to track clicks"

#: inc/settings-display.php:87
msgid ""
"To enable tracking of link click events in your website: 1. Open a website "
"page or message for editing; 2. In the text editor, select the link element "
"and click on the Finteza button; 3. Enter the click event name to be used in "
"statistics; 4. View event statistics in the <a href=https://panel.finteza."
"com target=_blank>Finteza dashboard</a>"
msgstr ""
"To enable tracking of link click events in your website:\n"
"\n"
"1. Open a website page or message for editing\n"
"2. In the text editor, select the link element and click on the Finteza "
"button\n"
"3. Enter the click event name to be used in statistics\n"
"4. View event statistics in the <a href=https://panel.finteza.com?"
"utm_source=wordpress.admin&utm_medium=link&utm_content=finteza.plugin."
"wordpress&utm_term=finteza.panel&utm_campaign=finteza.wordpress "
"target=_blank>Finteza dashboard</a>"

#: inc/settings-display.php:93
msgid "Where to view statistics"
msgstr "Where to view statistics"

